---
title: Fried Chicken & Cheesy Southern-Style Biscuits with Creamy Baby Leaf Slaw & Gravy
description: Get ready for a taste of Southern charm with crispy, golden chicken alongside flaky, buttery Southern-style biscuits with spring
onion and Cheddar cheese mixed through. This pairing is a match made in comfort food heaven!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6604fce3faa50670154dc0d4-325259d5.jpeg
